<CENTER><H1>WELCOME TO BERNARD CACHIA'S HOME PAGE</H1><P><HR>

<IMG SRC="bernar11.jpg" WIDTH=101 HEIGHT=127></CENTER>

<P>My name is Bernard Cachia. I would like to have your opinion on the following questions:
<P>1. Why is there something and not nothing?
<P>2. Does the Universe make any sense?
<P>3. Can the Universe exist independently of my perceptions of it?
<P>4. What does it mean not to exist?
