<HEAD>
<TITLE>MedGate</TITLE>
<!--Author of the initial cut presented during the Barcelona
conference, fall '95: Bas Klein, The North-South Centre
Date: 6 September 1995
Project: Medgate

Revised and graphically refined version, March '96 by
Obrad Bjelic-->
</HEAD>

<BODY BKCOLOR="#FFFFFF" BACKGROUND="Back.gif">
<IMG SRC="MedLogo.gif" ALT="MedGate" ALIGN=LEFT></IMG>
<IMG SRC="H_Welcom.gif">
<HR NOSHADE>
<BR>
MedGate is a joint  initiative by the
<A HREF="http://neon.coe.fr//NSCDATA/nshome.htm">North-South Centre</A>
of the Council of Europe, the <A HREF="http://www.unige.ch/mads">
Mediterranean Academy of Diplomatic Studies</A> in Malta and
the<A HREF=""> Centre d'Informaci i Documentaci Internacionales
a Barcelona</A>, which aims to help keeping you informed about what
is going on in the Mediterranean.
<P>
MedGate will help you find continously updated information
about social, economic, political, cultural and accademic events taking
place in the Mediterranean, as well as link you to the homepages of the
different organisations working on this issues in the Mediteranean.
<P>
MedGate has been structured to help you find the
information you need in the fastest posible way. Please click on one of the
following items to start your search:
<P>

<B>
<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER=0>
<TR><TH ALIGN=RIGHT>
    <A HREF="MedCal.htm">
    <B>Calendar</B>
    <IMG SRC="MedCal.gif" BORDER=0 WIDTH="64" HEIGHT="64" ALIGN=CENTER></A>
    <P>
<TD>
    <A HREF="WhoIsWho.htm">
    <IMG SRC="WhoIsWho.gif" BORDER=0 WIDTH="64" HEIGHT="64" ALIGN=CENTER>
    <B>Who is who?</B>
    </A>
    <P>
<TR><TH ALIGN=RIGHT>
    <A HREF="News.htm">
    <B>News and Facts</B>
    <IMG SRC="News.gif" BORDER=0 WIDTH="64" HEIGHT="64" ALIGN=CENTER></A>
    <P>
<TD>
    <A HREF="Map.htm">
    <IMG SRC="Map.gif" BORDER=0 WIDTH="64" HEIGHT="64" ALIGN=CENTER>
    <B>Countries</B>
    </A>
    <P>
<TR><TH ALIGN=RIGHT>
    <A HREF="Topics.htm">
    <B>Topics</B>
    <IMG SRC="Topics.gif" BORDER=0 WIDTH="64" HEIGHT="64" ALIGN=CENTER></A>
    <P>
<TD>
    <A HREF="tmplate3.htm">
    <IMG SRC="Publicat.gif" BORDER=0 WIDTH="64" HEIGHT="64" ALIGN=CENTER>
    <B>Publications</B>
    </A>
    <P>
</TABLE>
</CENTER>
</B>

