<I>Disclaimer: Medgate provides you with links to information and Web-pages of a wide array of organisations. The North-South Centre, nor any of the other initiative partners guarantee the correctness of the information provided nor the quality of the individual home pages MedGate can connect you with. Any information given reflects the opinion of the providing organisation alone and not necessarily that of the North-South Centre, the initiative partners or any other organisation participating in the MedGate project.<P>

Please contact the North-South Centre on the address mentioned below if you find any information on MedGate that is incorrect or outdated. Thanks.<P>
