<BODY>
<H2>Template for information on Organisations</H2>

This is a template for a WEB-page with information on your organisation. Please load this template in the HTML editor and fill in the information belwo. Please take care bnot to delete any of the HTML markers. e-mail this page to the North-South Centre or send it on diskette to the address below.<P>

<CENTER><H2>Please enter here the name of your organisation</H2></CENTER>

<CENTER><H4>Address:</H4></CENTER>

<CENTER>
Street and number<BR>
City and Postal Code<BR>
Country<BR>
Telefone:<BR>
Fax:<BR>
E-Mail:<BR>
</CENTER><P><BR>

<H4>Type of Organisation:</H4>

Please type on this place the type of your organisation (intergovernmental / governmental / international NGO / National NGO / etc.), plus any other relevant information describing the type of your organisation.<P><BR>

<H4>Working Areas:</H4>

Please type here the working areas / areas of interest of your organisation<P><BR>

<H3>MISSION STATEMENT</H3>

Please give here a short description of your organisation and the work it is doing.<P><BR>

