<h2 align=center><b><font COLOR="#000080"><font SIZE=+3>Regional Seminar
on the </font></font></b></h2>

<h1 align=center><b><font COLOR="#000080"><font SIZE=+4>Chemical Weapons
Convention</font></font></b></h1>

<h2 align=center><font COLOR="#000080"><font SIZE=+3>and its National Implementation</font></font></h2>

<h2 align=center><font COLOR="#000080">12 - 14 June 1996, Gozo, Malta</font>

<hr width="100%" ></h2>

<center><p><i><font COLOR="#008080"><font SIZE=+1>Organised by</font></font></i></p></center>

<center><p><font COLOR="#008080"><b><font SIZE=+2>The Multilateral Affairs
Directorate of the Ministry of Foreign Affairs</font><font SIZE=+1>, </font></b><font SIZE=+1>Valletta,
Malta</font></font></p></center>

<center><p><font COLOR="#008080"><font SIZE=+1>and</font></font></p></center>

<center><p><font COLOR="#008080"><font SIZE=+1>the provisional </font><b><font SIZE=+2>Technical
