<LI>Number of users
<LI>Networking ( LAN / WAN )
<LI>Internet connection
<LI>Security
<LI>Available software
<LI>Budget
</UL>

<H1>OS Protection &amp; Security</H1>

<UL>
<LI>Main factors:
<UL>
<LI>Good access control
<LI>Proper administration
<LI>Encrypted communication
</UL>

<LI>User checking:
<UL>
<LI>by &quot;something they know&quot; - password
<LI>by &quot;something they have&quot; - smartcard, token
<LI>by &quot;something they are&quot; - biometrics
</UL>

<LI>Kerberos ( RSA ), E-Mail PGP
</UL>

