<H2>      Office Automation </H2>
<HR>

<P>
Mr., Rodney James Naudi from Malta University presented his paper
on Office Automation. He stressed the importance to have Office
Automation due to the flowing:
<P>
 * Technology is evolving at a very fast rate
<P>
 * Advances improve on speed, accuracy, reliability and maintainability
<P>
 * Organization must keep barest with this new technology to be
able to compete`
<P>
 * Office automation has become commonplace within most organizations
<P>
Mr. Rodney also highlighted the benefits of Office Automation
:
<P>
 * Throughput
<P>
 * Efficiency
<P>
 * Productivity
<P>
But Office Automation involves the flowing hidden cost:
<P>
 * Related Strain Injury (RSI)
<P>
 * Dissatisfaction at work
<P>
 * Increased frustration
<P>
 * Impersonal approach
<P>
 * Decrease in job opportunities
<P>
In conclusion Mr.Rodney emphasized the need to keep pace with
developments of IT. 
</BODY>

